  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Saturday. Dad had one clear target for this weekend: hike up to one of the highest mountain trails on the island before winter fully ended.",
      "zh": "星期六。爸爸這個週末有一個明確的目標：在冬天完全結束前，去爬島上其中一條海拔最高的登山步道。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The trail began on a narrow, rocky path, winding through thick forest before opening onto steep, wooden walkways built along the mountainside.",
      "zh": "步道一開始是一條狹窄多石的小徑，穿過茂密的森林，接著轉為沿著山坡搭建的陡峭木製步道。"
    },
    {
      "en": "About halfway up, we found the source of a small mountain stream, cold water bubbling straight out of the rock itself.",
      "zh": "大約走到一半，我們找到一條小小山溪的源頭，冰冷的溪水直接從岩石裡冒出來。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William insisted on drinking straight from the stream, and Dad had to explain, patiently, why that was not a great idea up here.",
      "zh": "William 堅持要直接從溪裡喝水，爸爸只好耐心地解釋，為什麼在這個高度這樣做不太妙。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The trail took a sharp bend near a steel railing, protecting hikers from a drop that suddenly felt much higher than it had looked from below.",
      "zh": "步道在一個裝有鋼製護欄的地方轉了個急彎，護欄保護著登山客，避免摔落一段從山下看起來根本沒那麼高的落差。"
    },
    {
      "en": "As we climbed higher, the air grew noticeably colder, and by the final stretch, a light dusting of snow, maybe an inch deep, covered the ground.",
      "zh": "越往上爬，空氣明顯變得更冷，走到最後一段路，地上覆蓋著一層薄薄的雪，大概只有一英吋深。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I had never actually touched real snow before, and I will admit I stood there a little too long, just letting it melt slowly in my hand.",
      "zh": "我以前從沒真的摸過真正的雪，我得承認，我在那裡站了有點太久，就只是讓雪慢慢在我手心融化。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William threw a small, poorly formed snowball at me, and I threw one back, both of us instantly forgetting how tired our legs actually were.",
      "zh": "William 朝我丟了一顆形狀很糟的小雪球，我也丟了一顆回去，我們兩個都瞬間忘了自己的腿其實有多累。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Near the summit, a small wooden sign and a faded flag marked the exact highest point, and a small crowd of hikers took turns taking photos beside it.",
      "zh": "接近山頂的地方，有一個小小的木牌和一面褪色的旗子標示出最高點，一小群登山客輪流在旁邊拍照。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The sun broke through the clouds right as we reached the top, and for one instant, the whole view below shone in a way that made the whole climb worth it.",
      "zh": "我們抵達山頂的那一刻，太陽剛好從雲層中露出來，就那麼一瞬間，下方整片景色閃耀著，讓這趟辛苦的攀爬完全值得了。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A cold wind blew steadily across the peak, strong enough that Sophia's warning about wearing extra layers suddenly made a lot more sense.",
      "zh": "一陣冷風持續吹過山頂，強到讓 Sophia 之前叮嚀我們多穿幾層的話，突然變得非常有道理。"
    },
    {
      "en": "My face felt a little sunburned despite the cold, an odd combination Dad said happens often at this height, where the sun burns you even in freezing air.",
      "zh": "儘管天氣很冷，我的臉還是有點曬傷，爸爸說在這個海拔常常會有這種奇怪的組合，即使空氣冷得要命，太陽還是會把你曬傷。"
    },
    {
      "en": "A small group of deer grazed calmly near the trailhead on our way back down, barely bothered by hikers passing just a few meters away.",
      "zh": "下山的路上，靠近步道口的地方，一小群鹿正安靜地吃著草，幾乎不在意幾公尺外經過的登山客。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the time we reached the car, my legs were sore enough that I had to rub my calves for several minutes just to feel normal again.",
      "zh": "等我們回到車上，我的腿痠到得揉了好幾分鐘小腿，才總算感覺恢復正常。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William, meanwhile, fell asleep almost instantly, curled up sideways, still smelling faintly of cold mountain air and melted snow.",
      "zh": "同時，William 幾乎是秒睡，整個人側躺蜷縮著，身上還隱約帶著冰冷山風和融雪的味道。"
    },
    {
      "en": "That night, Sophia gave us both a sour plum candy each, saying it always helps tired legs recover faster, a claim I have no way to prove or disprove.",
      "zh": "那天晚上，Sophia 給了我們每人一顆酸梅糖，說這對疲累的腿恢復有幫助，這個說法我完全沒辦法證明或反駁。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Lesson of the day: reaching a target this high in the cold and snow felt harder than almost anything else I have done this year, and somehow that made it better.",
      "zh": "今日心得：在寒冷和雪地中抵達這麼高的一個目標，感覺比我今年做過的幾乎任何事都還難，而不知怎麼地，這反而讓一切變得更好。"
    }
  ],
